# counselor API Keys
# Copy this file to .Renviron and fill in your actual keys
# NEVER commit .Renviron with real keys!

# Anthropic - for Claude conversation intelligence
# Get yours at: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key-here

# Deepgram - for speech-to-text
# Get yours at: https://console.deepgram.com/
DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=your-deepgram-key-here

# Cartesia - for text-to-speech
# Get yours at: https://cartesia.ai/
CARTESIA_API_KEY=your-cartesia-key-here
